{"tid":1262701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢佬自己搭巴士搭過龍 竟連環屌人老母逾三十連發","createTime":"2019-06-27T20:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T23:31:09.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35feb02bfe7f6302636b39ad98255aec90f326d8","tid":1262701,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T20:58:28.000Z","msg":"本以為今日會平安大吉，點知去到加走時段又發生屌老母事件<br />\n<br />\n約凌晨1:40分，一部N216加班車駛入油塘總站，我打算前去同該車長打招呼，點知佢行出黎同我講話有個痴線佬，兄弟有難，咁<br />\n我即刻過去了解事件<br />\n<br />\n因部車既報站壞左，所以阿伯過左站，由去彩雲變去左油塘，原本打算叫佢搭返即班N216返去彩雲<br />\n<br />\n點知佢又屌老母又喊打喊殺，冷靜唔到，我都十分擔心佢身體狀況，最後決定報警處理<br />\n<br />\n#阿伯坐過站大鬧巴士車長<br />\n#阿伯以前係警察wo<br />\n#二個被屌好過一個被屌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/830890643623185/posts/2325289297516638?s=753094347&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F830890643623185%2Fposts%2F2325289297516638%3Fs%3D753094347%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=2d4947e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/830890643623185/posts/2325289297516638?s=753094347&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"85b1bfbd921623ddd9b9c0c1e426d69d8ddbd840","tid":1262701,"uid":226959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T21:03:18.000Z","msg":"笑到我噴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d9472d7956237c94b090ca0feae9a025dc99c2","tid":1262701,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T22:33:50.000Z","msg":"屌穿?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60af502b60114979c73073c02a442dfe6d0096b","tid":1262701,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T22:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6EMWD_kBnfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F